RUN /bin/sh -c dnf update -y && dnf install -y   ca-certificates   findutils   gnupg   hostname   tar   udev   which   curl   iproute   && dnf clean all   && echo $'#!/bin/sh
set -e
set -u
n=0
max=2
until [ $n -gt $max ]; do
  set +e
  (
    dnf update -y &&
    dnf install -y "$@"
  )
  CODE=$?
  set -e
  if [ $CODE -eq 0 ]; then
    break
  fi
  if [ $n -eq $max ]; then
    exit $CODE
  fi
  echo "dnf failed, retrying"
  n=$(($n + 1))
done
dnf clean all' > /usr/sbin/install_packages   && chmod 0755 "/usr/sbin/install_packages" # buildkit
